						               													<description>XAGA- Das Stadtspiel is a creative boardgame. The game begins with a city that wants more color from ideas and strategies. Variety is desired, because instead of quantity the citizens are concerned with the quality of the city. On the city-plan, the players alter buildings, plants and so on, and attempt to bring in inhabitants and guests. However the building alone are not sufficient. A clever and imaginative advertisement is fundamental to winning the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the constant role-change between investor and inhabitant the players together create their own place of fantasy and strategy. Communication is very important! The end the election for the &amp;quot;Citizen of Honor&amp;quot; decides the win. To win the title, one does not only need the votes, but also the &amp;quot;most buildings&amp;quot;, the &amp;quot;most beautiful house&amp;quot;, the &amp;quot;most disturbing neighbor&amp;quot; and several other categories.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
